<h2>What’s new in 0.2.5</h2><ul>
<li>Fixed: Design mode now clears stuck reveal blur so selected pages stay sharp.</li>
<li>Fixed: Expired Claude sign-ins now show the real authentication error and the correct claude auth login action.</li>
<li>Fixed: Authentication failures no longer appear as completed agent progress.</li>
<li>Improved: Failed focused edits keep the exact selected target and protect the last working source.</li>
</ul>
